(I) ARE NOT CANDIDATES FOR POSITIONS ON THE GOVERNING
BODY OF THE HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION IN THAT ELECTION; AND
(II) DO NOT HAVE A CONFLICT OF INTEREST REGARDING ANY
CANDIDATE IN THE ELECTION.
